{"tid":2045732,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"早買早享受，遲買貴幾舊！MacBook Pro 改配 16GB RAM 費用增加一倍","createTime":"2020-06-01T03:42:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T15:47:23.000Z","uid":109923,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"56500c13c4212449458329728b058ca6c4ffe682","tid":2045732,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T03:42:16.000Z","msg":"網站 MacRumors 發現 Apple 官方網站的 13 吋 MacBook Pro 購買頁面，記憶體升級的選項突然大幅加價。顧客打算將 8GB RAM 增加至 16GB RAM，原本只需額外支付 100 美元（約 775 港元），現在則需要支付 200 美元（1,551 港元）。<br />\n<br />\n加價似乎並不局限於北美市場，就連歐洲和其他市場亦同樣加倍，以歐盟為例，由 8GB 升級至 16GB RAM，就由原來的 125 歐元增加至 250 歐元，至於香港市場的價格，筆者撰稿時跟歐美市場相若，升級至 16GB RAM 需要額外支付 1,500 港元。MacRumors 指新產品推出不久就加價相當不尋常，認為 Apple 可能面對突如其來的成本上漲，於是將之轉嫁予消費者，希望 Apple 能夠透露突然加價背後的原因。<br />\n<br />\n來源：ilounge"},{"pid":"306407c058c622c89888d6f6e79effa5076d2f1c","tid":2045732,"uid":94828,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T03:49:11.000Z","msg":"Apple爸爸想加就加架啦<br />\n唔係要問i9意見呀？"},{"pid":"d2e7f3d1f4da1a7cba958cdff10e8bad31f307e1","tid":2045732,"uid":113922,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T06:21:00.000Z","msg":"腦場8g  ram 價250"},{"pid":"bfa9f89fa01c7c0643253c08071f9b8d1b0d59c6","tid":2045732,"uid":57677,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T06:36:27.000Z","msg":"生活態度無價<br />\n<br />\n好似啲人玩音響, 一條線五萬蚊,不過原來橡膠多個銅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02aa0997e462cbad5caeeb1d0f96086ba540f124","tid":2045732,"uid":308964,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"bfa9f89fa01c7c0643253c08071f9b8d1b0d59c6","tid":2045732,"uid":57677,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T06:36:27.000Z","msg":"生活態度無價<br />\n<br />\n好似啲人玩音響, 一條線五萬蚊,不過原來橡膠多個銅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T07:11:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets